    "We aim to illustrate the creation of such a system with a case study to provide orientation for practitioners by implementing such a system for one particular task.",
    "This results in two concrete research goals.",
    "On the one hand, the components we implement for the system need to be evaluated.",
    "On the other hand, the reception of the feedback by learners also needs evaluation.",
    "Accordingly, we address the following research questions in this study."
  ]
}